title: DDFP 419: Wild Card Preview & AJ Hawk
itunes:title: DDFP 419: Wild Card Preview & AJ Hawk
description:
Shek sits down with Handsome Hank and Matt "Money" Smith to preview the upcoming Wild Card matchups. The guys talk about the Seattle Seahawks, Antonio Brown, J.J. Watt, and Adrian Peterson. Plus, and exclusive interview with Cincinnati's AJ Hawk. Can the Seahawks win in Minnesota? Find out more on DDFP.   Watch the full show here (6pm ET): https://youtu.be/_0zTwtAQbA4
